des:
The TEA is an entertainment news brief brought to you from Los Angeles, CA. This program is for bored, fun or lonely people who want their dose of Hollywood and popular culture. 

We'll talk about the things that make us laugh, scream and cry in pop culture and the news. The TEA is hosted by entertainment news aficionado Issen. 

The TEA is an entertainment news aggregrator, find all your TEA in one place at www.thetea.net. Do you have something you want to share ? Email us at thetea.tips@gmail.com Don't forget to rate this program. Sit back relax and sip on this TEA!
